# Snake Game - Implementation Guide

## Core Game Mechanics

- **Speed System**: 
  - Starts at 5, capped at 25
  - Each level adds 2 to speed
  - Different fruits per speed increase based on difficulty

## Fruit Spawning Rules

- Each fruit should ONLY appear in its specific level
- Fruits per level:
  - Easy Mode: Each fruit appears exactly 6 times in its level
  - Medium Mode: Each fruit appears exactly 7 times in its level
  - Hard Mode: 
    - Passion Fruit (Level 11): 3 times
    - Papaya (Level 12): 3 times
    - Starfruit (Level 13): 3 times
    - Dragon Fruit (Level 14): 3 times
    - Banana (Level 15): 1 time

